      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition vehicle that shows extremely well and should satisfy a buyer looking for a standout example. It runs and drives beautifully, feels tight and well-sorted, and presents with outstanding cosmetic and interior condition throughout. This is not a project or a driver with excuses\u2014it is a truly high-quality vehicle that has clearly been cared for and should be ready to enjoy immediately.",
