    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and honest transportation for the budget-minded buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a practical project, commuter backup, or around-town runabout with strong value at this price point. It shows its age and will benefit from attention, but for the right buyer it represents a cost-effective way to get into a vehicle without overspending. Priced to sell and well-suited for someone who appreciates straightforward value.",
