    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, parts car, or simple runaround with potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s got honest value for the right buyer and could be a great fit for someone handy or needing a budget-friendly option. A straightforward car being offered as-is, priced to sell, and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and a chassis that still feels composed on the road. This car shows its age cosmetically and will benefit from some TLC, but it offers dependable start-up, usable power, and a practical platform for someone who wants affordable transportation or a straightforward restoration candidate. A great way to get into a capable vehicle without spending big money.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car. Sold as-is, priced to move fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of well-worn character that tells a story the moment you see it. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom-perfect\u2014what it offers is presence, personality, and real potential for the right buyer. Whether you need an affordable runabout, a hands-on project, or a vehicle with old-school charm and plenty of life left to give, this one invites someone practical and imaginative to make it their own. A chance to get into a distinctive car without a big upfront spend.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a straightforward value choice for a buyer seeking affordable transportation or a solid project. It offers honest utility, a comfortable cabin, and the kind of price point that makes ownership easy to justify. A sensible option for someone who appreciates value and opportunity in one package.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for simple, affordable wheels that can get the job done without breaking the bank? This car isn\u2019t perfect, and I\u2019d rather be upfront about that, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy runaround. It has the kind of everyday wear you\u2019d expect, but at this price it\u2019s a chance to grab a car for real-world money. If you want something cheap, honest, and worth a look, come take a peek.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project with strong enthusiast appeal and a surprisingly honest mechanical feel. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still has the kind of direct road feedback that makes these worth saving. Cosmetics and overall condition reflect age and use, so expect a driver-level/project presentation, but the core package is there: a complete car with good bones, usable running gear, and plenty of upside for someone who wants an affordable entry point. Great candidate for a budget build, weekend fixer, or parts-preserving restoration.",
      "price": 7900.0,
